      "description": "Monte Carlo sampling (n=500) was performed across inlet flow rate, rotational speed, and blood viscosity distributions. Predicted hemolysis index distributions are reported. No sensitivity ranking of input parameters was derived from this analysis; dominant drivers of output variance remain uncharacterized."
    },
    {
