      "name": "Experimental comparison — FDA benchmark pump hemolysis data",
      "description": "Predicted normalized index of hemolysis (NIH) compared against published FDA benchmark experimental data at three operating conditions. Mean absolute error 18%; systematic over-prediction observed at high-shear conditions."
    }
  ],
