      "rationale": "Validation performed on FDA generic pump geometry under steady bovine blood conditions. COU geometry is a proprietary centrifugal design with different impeller clearances. Geometric and fluid similarity gaps reduce relevance. Achieved level 2 against required level 5."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
