      "rationale": "No independent analyst review of model setup has been performed. Boundary condition assignment and hemolysis post-processing scripts not independently verified. Epistemic gap at MRL 5. Achieved level 1 against required level 4."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Model form",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 5,
      "achievedLevel": 1,
      "factorStatus": "not-assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Turbulence model and hemolysis constitutive law must be justified against physiological data; alternative model forms must be evaluated.",
      "rationale": "SST k-omega turbulence model selected without systematic comparison to alternative closures. Giersiepen-Wurzinger hemolysis power law used without evaluation of alternative formulations. Model form uncertainty not quantified. Epistemic gap at MRL 5. Achieved level 1 against required level 5."
    },
